sentences: After a 1981 American tour, he retired from the experimental music scene and dropped off the public radar.
Wilson then lapsed into obscurity until around 1996, when Beck was heard citing him as an influence in concerts, at award ceremonies, and on his album, Odelay.
In the early 2000s, Motel Records began a search to find the reclusive musician, but were unsuccessful (even after hiring a private detective).
